{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Provide interest-free Renewable Energy Assistance Loan during energy crisis.",
        "additional_details": "A simple plan that benefits everyone:\r\n\r\nHouseholds \u2013 Immediate cash savings vs paying hefty bills to energy suppliers; less dependency on the grid; no-interest cost on buying expensive equipment. \r\n\r\nGovernment \u2013  Reduction in inflation; the UK can become energy secure in a few years, also meeting its climate targets \r\n\r\nSuppliers \u2013 They can buy excess energy from households at a low cost; they can work with the government in installation, maintenance, billing, and awareness-building.",
        "background": "A win-win plan that gives immediate and long-term benefits: \r\nGovernment to provide interest-free loans to homes for installing renewable energy equipment (solar panel, heat pump, retrofit).\r\nThis will reduce monthly utility bills for homes. The savings can repay the loan over 5-7 years.",
